{"tid":302442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 藏航拍遙控器利刀現身西九　青山派中出羊子被捕","createTime":"2017-06-29T11:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T13:51:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"839d9092c122e8f5ab13d458d796f7acbdacefa0","tid":302442,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170629182728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170629182728&h=d956cb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平下午視察西九文化區，警方全日在西九龍一帶加強戒備巡邏，早上10時在西隧九龍出口附近發現港獨人士「中出羊子」形迹可疑，上前截查後在他身上搜出一部懷疑航拍機遙控器、天線、鎅刀、剪刀及膠索，經調查後以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器將他拘捕，押返尖沙咀警署扣查，案件交由油尖警區重案組跟進。警方經追查後，下午在其大角咀寓所搜出航拍機。 <br />\n<br />\n常作古代女性打扮的「中出羊子」，原名鍾銘麟。今晨9時許，他在社交網站facebook分享最新消息，先上載一張在梳士巴利道的渡輪指示牌相片，並留言稱︰「何日到彼岸。」之後又上載了一張尖沙咀海港城對開港威大道停車場海旁相片。網友紛紛留言，有人說：「咁早起身，必有事發生！」另有人留言：「 渡輪上，懷念你說生如戰士。」惟他其後未有回應。 <br />\n<br />\n早上10時，警方派員在西九龍一帶巡邏期間，在雅翔道及柯士甸道西交界、即西隧收費站附近，發現身穿T恤牛仔褲及孭背囊的「中出羊子」在附近形迹可疑，遂上前截停他及進行搜身，結果在他背囊內發現一部懷疑航拍機遙控器、兩組分別增強手機及WiFi信號的天線、一把鎅刀、一把剪刀及一批膠索帶，但未有發現航拍機。警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器將他拘捕，並將他押返警署作進一步調查。警方下午掩至其大角咀寓所搜獲航拍機，已檢走調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_04p.jpg?20170629182728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20170629182728&h=3175306c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_05p.jpg?20170629182728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20170629182728&h=b050554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_06p.jpg?20170629182728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20170629182728&h=e84efc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_07p.jpg?20170629182728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20170629182728&h=696b9944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_10p.jpg?20170629182728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629165555456-0629_00822_001_10p.jpg%3F20170629182728&h=fdf83e3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee950a184b49dcb74c8249238aa611e59137e91a","tid":302442,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"傻架佢"},{"pid":"f2b80bce063ed06f1d47b59206304d209063bcd8","tid":302442,"uid":7996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實身上有鎅刀同較剪就犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前個生果乜乜乜帶著生果刀危險 都冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9383f3543cf8f0d22ff0c5902f39bcb7132a29","tid":302442,"uid":33612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"最尾果張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d5f86df22b1ee208525d24ae46efe9cf0c070d","tid":302442,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實身上有鎅刀同較剪就犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n